# Claude context exclusions for token efficiency.
#
# CLAUDE.md's Wave Index points at one wave file at a time. The "completed" wave
# files (and standing-rules) are excluded by default so Claude doesn't load
# them on every session. When working on a specific completed wave (e.g. for
# audit / regression triage), explicitly Read the file instead of relying on
# context auto-load.
#
# The CURRENT WAVE FILE (per CLAUDE.md "Launch Plan — Current Wave") is NOT
# excluded so it loads naturally during launch-plan work.

